The paper deals with pre-training in reinforcement learning, which is a subfield of machine learning. The paper proposes a new method called tiMe, which combines ideas from Batch RL and Meta RL. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.RO (Robotics). The paper also deals with control tasks, which suggests that it could be categorized under cs.SY (Systems and Control) or cs.LO (Optimization and Control).
